# Data Analysis Dashboard - User Stories

## Core User Stories

### Data Input & Setup

- As a user, I want to upload any CSV/Excel file so I can analyze my own data
- As a user, I want to use sample data so I can test the system before using my data
- As a user, I want to see file upload progress so I know when my data is ready
- As a user, I want immediate feedback if my file has issues so I can fix them quickly

### Basic Analysis

- As a user, I want to select analysis types from suggestions so I can quickly start analyzing
- As a user, I want to write custom analysis prompts so I can get specific insights
- As a user, I want to compare different metrics so I can understand relationships in my data
- As a user, I want to filter data by any column so I can focus on specific segments

### Data Visualization

- As a user, I want to see my analysis results in charts so I can understand patterns visually
- As a user, I want to switch between chart types so I can view data in different ways
- As a user, I want to download charts as images so I can use them in presentations
- As a user, I want to view multiple charts at once so I can compare different aspects

### AI-Powered Analysis

- As a user, I want to ask questions in plain English so I can analyze without technical knowledge
- As a user, I want automated insights so I can quickly understand my data
- As a user, I want pattern detection so I can identify trends automatically
- As a user, I want anomaly detection so I can spot unusual patterns

### Data Interaction

- As a user, I want to interact with charts so I can explore data points in detail
- As a user, I want to drill down into specific data segments so I can investigate further
- As a user, I want to save my analyses so I can refer to them later
- As a user, I want to export results so I can share them with others

### User Experience

- As a user, I want a clean interface so I can find features easily
- As a user, I want clear loading indicators so I know when processing is happening
- As a user, I want helpful error messages so I can resolve issues myself
- As a user, I want tooltips and help text so I can learn while using the system

### Performance

- As a user, I want quick response times so I can work efficiently
- As a user, I want to analyze large datasets without crashes so I can work with real-world data
- As a user, I want to run multiple analyses simultaneously so I can be more productive
- As a user, I want auto-save so I don't lose my work

### Customization

- As a user, I want to customize chart colors so they match my preferences
- As a user, I want to save favorite analyses so I can reuse them
- As a user, I want to set default views so I can start working quickly
- As a user, I want to customize data formats so they match my needs

### Collaboration

- As a user, I want to share my analyses with colleagues so we can work together
- As a user, I want to export my findings in different formats so I can use them elsewhere
- As a user, I want to add comments to analyses so I can explain my insights
- As a user, I want to see analysis history so I can track changes

### Mobile Access

- As a user, I want to view analyses on my mobile device so I can access insights anywhere
- As a user, I want responsive charts so I can read them on any screen size
- As a user, I want touch-friendly controls so I can interact on mobile devices
- As a user, I want to receive notifications so I know when analyses are complete
